    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >StarSim: BattleZone是一款设定在StarSim宇宙中的即时战略（RTS）游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏玩法包括经典的RTS机制，如：建造基地、收集资源、研究新技术、建造防御、训练单位等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295350/extras/5f372c33d22aa925d352dad7078d5847.poster.avif?t=1772486667\" width=854 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295350/extras/5f372c33d22aa925d352dad7078d5847.webm?t=1772486667\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295350/extras/5f372c33d22aa925d352dad7078d5847.mp4?t=1772486667\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您将指挥Home Ascolate的部队，以控制资源丰富的无人星球。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295350/extras/695b6a3ed76b39e2a25d1bf26691e4b2.poster.avif?t=1772486667\" width=854 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295350/extras/695b6a3ed76b39e2a25d1bf26691e4b2.webm?t=1772486667\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295350/extras/695b6a3ed76b39e2a25d1bf26691e4b2.mp4?t=1772486667\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战役模式包含故事驱动的任务，展示Home Ascolate与其他派系之间的冲突。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295350/extras/3e1525485c44a8e17cf67acc3f533188.poster.avif?t=1772486667\" width=854 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295350/extras/3e1525485c44a8e17cf67acc3f533188.webm?t=1772486667\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295350/extras/3e1525485c44a8e17cf67acc3f533188.mp4?t=1772486667\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏还包含遭遇战模式，玩家可以在不同的地图上设置并进行自定义战斗，与不同情境下的敌人交战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295350/extras/ec239d89a351144a3203da66e14c267a.avif?t=1772486667\" width=800 height=77 /></span></p>",
